Improvements/Refinements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

+ heatmaps / function plotImage
  - make simple function to get rid of technical nightmares when using R's
    builtin image function to represent heatmaps with precomputer colors
  - finish implementing a plotImage function to avoid indexing nightmares with
    the builtin image function when using precomputed colors
  - implement interval percentages in the legend as was done with fireplots
  - link new function histogram2D with plotImage and makeColors

+ venn diagrams
  - add extra layouts for initial positions (horizontal, vertical, diagonal)
  - add generalized linear layout using angle parameter to control orientation

+ color Legend
  - add title
  - add units (optional)
  - management of extrema (represent below and above areas)
  - see if possible to plot color legend outside of plot area (right margin)

+ transparency
  - consider adding a transparency (alpha) attribute to group colors

+ extend color transformations
  - support transparency transformations
  - support standard color filters as available in the Processing language
  - support color "morphing"
    use source color and target color to transform colors accordingly (either
    in HSV or RGB space)

+ extend group symbols
  - support dual color symbols with outline using pairs of graphic symbols
    (e.g empty square + filled square, empty circle + filled circle )

================================================================================
New features
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
+ venn diagrams
  - design an evolutionnary algorithm that encode the structure and evolution
    of populations of generative initial layouts
    chromosomes:
      1. order of elements in layouts
      2. hierarchy of layouts
      3. layout functions
    fitness:
      1. residual energy after layout optimization
      2. similarity beween initial and optimal layout
      3. optimization time
    diversity:

+ color management
  - provide guidance to match color scale parameters / represented values
    (plot distribution, find modes, quantiles, etc...)

+ consider extending color transformation:
  - define color filters (collections of transformation parameters) to make it
    easier to apply and chain complex color transformations

+ consider extending color generation:
  - concepts from the colorspace package (categorical, sequential, divergent)
  - concepts from the colortools package (complementary, triadic, tetradic)
  - concepts from the dichromat package (color blindness)
  - consider introducing a concept of maximal separation given style constraints
    use optimization strategy in data and color space to achieve maximal color
    separation and readability for categorical data and numerical data (density)

+ consider extending group representation and color mapping with
  cascading/functional styles

+ consider support for point size mapping and corresponding legend generator

+ layouts
  - automated placement of labels and legends could be proposed according to
    density of represented elements

+ consider builtin support for common plots
  - histograms and density plots (1D)
  - density scatterplots (2D)

+ consider builtin support for circular plots

